## ğŸ”§ Technical Details

### **Component Structure**
```javascript
<VLSMDesigner>
  â”œâ”€ GameMenu (scenario selection)
  â”œâ”€ GameHeader (stats, network info)
  â”œâ”€ GameContainer
  â”‚   â”œâ”€ DepartmentsPanel (left)
  â”‚   â”œâ”€ ConfigurationPanel (center)
  â”‚   â””â”€ VisualizationPanel (right)
  â”œâ”€ FeedbackToast (notifications)
  â”œâ”€ CompletionModal (results screen)
  â”œâ”€ ControlBar (hints, reset)
  â””â”€ HintPanel (collapsible tips)
</VLSMDesigner>
```

### **Key Functions**

**calculateSubnetMask(hostsNeeded)**
- Determines optimal prefix length
- Returns prefix, usable hosts, dotted decimal

**calculateSubnetAddresses(baseAddress, prefix)**
- Calculates network address
- Determines first/last usable IPs
- Finds broadcast address
- Returns next subnet start

**checkOverlaps(newSubnet, existingSubnets)**
- Detects address space conflicts
- Prevents overlapping allocations
- Returns conflicting subnet if found

